        public double calculateTax(double flatCharge,
                           double rateBetween150000And400000,

                           double cityTax,
                           double largeTownTax,
                           double smallTownTax,
                           double villageTax,
                           double countrysideTax,
                           double pprTax)
        Method for testing experimental tax rates from a different tax calculation formula
        Parameters:
        flatCharge - flat tax charge
        rateBetween150000And400000 - percentage of market value (0.xx)
        rateBetween400000And650000 - percentage of market value (0.xx
        rateAbove650000 - percentage of market value (0.xx
        cityTax - charge to be paid if located in a city
        largeTownTax - charge to be paid if located in a large town
        smallTownTax - charge to be paid if located in a small town
        villageTax - charge to be paid if located in a village
        countrysideTax - charge to be paid if located in the countryside
        pprTax - charge to be paid if principle private residence
        Returns:
        returns the theoretical tax value using the experimental tax calculation
